@SeaRoth lol that's been the struggle.

@stevemessick closing and re-opening projects did not work.

I did finally find a way to stop the poltergeist was to kill my `.idea` folder completely and then re-activate the flutter and dart plugins, this was suggested by @tamcy  [here](https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/2017#issuecomment-376749910)
